{
  "stem": "7455.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's not going to come to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They got busy, and we moved into the cellar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then the Germans issued orders-- a curfew at 4:00.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There's not to be-- no Jew is to be in the street because they'll be shot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In the summ-- in the summer, it's-- the sun is shining, daylight.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We cannot dare-- we don't dare to stick our heads out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Besides, with the house that was burned down, there was like a skeleton of a house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The windows burned out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was just outlines of windows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And where we were, we didn't want anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the whole neighborhood was burned out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was like a shelter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were-- felt safe, that nobody knows that behind, in the back of that house, there's an entrance to a cellar.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was a window to the street, so my father cut out that window and filled it up with bricks, that the front street should not have been visible that somebody is there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So it was just like a ruin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Nobody would know that we are there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to-- we were not allowed to be in the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now if we had to go in the street, they issued that every Jew has to wear an armband with a star of David.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So from sheets, we cut out strips, and we were sewing and embroidering like a little star of David.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were afraid to walk the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was full of military, and they occupied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Gestapo was there occupying quarters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after a few days, things normalized, which means whoever had a home that did not burn down had a home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stayed in our ruin.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
